import React from 'react'; import '../index.css'; function Card(props) { const styles = { redHoverbutton: style({ backgroundColor: "#aaaaaa", fontSize: "1.1rem", transition: "all ease .5s", ":hover": { backgroundColor: "#ff0000", color: "#ffffff" } }) }; return ( <> {/*

{props.id}

{props.title}

Name: {props.sname}

Price: {props.price} pkr

*/}

Brand :{props.sname}

Title: {props.title}

{props.price} {props.sale_price}
) } export default Card;
